      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t媒体报道的准确性确实非常重要，这是新闻三要素之一<br/>\n<br/>\n然而人非圣贤，孰能无过。作为一个媒体，有错能承认，能改正，并且为严重错误而致歉，善莫大焉。<br/>\n<br/>\n我一直觉得以BBC为首的英国主流媒体在报道的公正性和中立性和遣词造句的典雅性上，要超过VOA（VOA中文一股海外民运味）和法广（RFI中文的有些文章写的实在太跳脱）<br/>\n<br/>\nBBC曾经有一篇关于涿州水灾的报道，把涿州写成了Zhouzhou，经过我指正之后承认错误并且修正为Zhuozhou<br/>\n<br/>\n这是BBC的原文，现在已经修改完成  <a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmJjLmNvLnVrL25ld3Mvd29ybGQtYXNpYS1jaGluYS02NjM2OTEzNw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-66369137\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-66369137</a><br/>\n<br/>\n这是另外一个网站当时直接从BBC搬运的文章， 现在还保留着BBC当时的把涿州写成Zhouzhou的错误<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2F1ZGlnYXpldHRlLmNvbS5zYS9hcnRpY2xlLzYzNDY0Mg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.saudigazette.com.sa/article/634642\">https://www.saudigazette.com.sa/article/634642</a><br/>\n<br/>\n以下是我的纠错反馈和他们给我的反馈记录<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9RN3JaUnJjLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q7rZRrc.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q7rZRrc.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q7rZRrc.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS81SEVFWTM0LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/5HEEY34.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5HEEY34.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5HEEY34.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>从中可以看出他们不仅有着接收普罗大众纠错的意愿，也有着成熟的处理管道以及“Your comments have been placed on our audience feedback report to be seen by senior management across the BBC and the BBC News website editors.”这样的引以为戒的措施。\t\t</div>",
